<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCowdery1834" class="citation news cs1">Cowdery, Oliver (September 7, 1834). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.josephsmithpapers.org/paper-summary/history-1834-1836/50">"Letter to William W. Phelps"</a>. <i>Messenger and Advocate</i>. pp.&#160;48–49<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">September 11,</span> 2022</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Messenger+and+Advocate&amp;rft.atitle=Letter+to+William+W.+Phelps&amp;rft.pages=48-49&amp;rft.date=1834-09-07&amp;rft.aulast=Cowdery&amp;rft.aufirst=Oliver&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.josephsmithpapers.org%2Fpaper-summary%2Fhistory-1834-1836%2F50&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMelchizedek+priesthood+%28Latter+Day+Saints%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
